{"id":"UEUTGkxp4oBI9Nqq","meta":{"instanceId":"d10cee5850f40500b6ac1fe1ba504620ef7ac5eb64c7ae29b76c4e81f4d927b3"},"name":"Sort Typeform survey responses and draft replies with GPT-4o-mini","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"6c600209-0941-4f7d-ad72-fbcaeafb9999","name":"Sticky Note","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-3856,-1584],"parameters":{"width":480,"height":896,"content":"## Sort Typeform survey responses and draft replies with GPT-4o-mini\n\n### How it works\n\nThis workflow listens for new Typeform survey responses, extracts key fields, and uses OpenAI to classify the respondent’s sentiment. Negative responses are routed into an empathetic draft-and-human-approval loop with Slack notifications before sending and CRM logging, while positive responses receive an automatically generated thank-you email and are logged separately. A standalone configuration node stores workflow variables such as form, sheet, tab, and Slack channel identifiers.\n\n### Setup steps\n\n- Connect Typeform credentials and select the survey form that should trigger the workflow.\n- Configure OpenAI credentials and ensure the classification and email-drafting prompts use the intended GPT-4o-mini model/settings.\n- Connect Slack credentials and set the alert/review channel in the workflow variables.\n- Connect Gmail credentials for sending respondent emails.\n- Connect Google Sheets credentials and set the target spreadsheet ID and tab name for CRM logging.\n- Update the Configure Workflow Variables node with typeformFormId, googleSheetId, sheetTabName, and slackChannelSurveyAlerts values, and verify field names in the extraction code match the Typeform response schema.\n\n### Customization\n\nAdjust the sentiment criteria, email prompts, Slack approval message format, and CRM columns to match the team’s escalation process and customer communication style."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"90b3d430-7235-4fd8-b768-e44faa64e498","name":"Sticky Note1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-2768,-1520],"parameters":{"color":7,"height":448,"content":"## Configure workflow variables\n\nStandalone setup cluster that defines shared IDs and names used elsewhere, including the Typeform form, Google Sheet, sheet tab, and Slack survey alert channel."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"ba405712-eacf-4f75-8aaf-22d37250babe","name":"Sticky Note2","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-3296,-944],"parameters":{"color":"#020000","width":416,"height":320,"content":"## Receive survey response\n\nStarts the workflow from a new Typeform submission and extracts the respondent fields needed for sentiment analysis and follow-up emails."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c3718646-b10c-4a17-bd98-edc6575d7e75","name":"Sticky Note3","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-2848,-912],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":768,"height":304,"content":"## Classify and route sentiment\n\nUses OpenAI to classify the extracted survey response, cleans the model output, and branches the workflow based on whether the sentiment is negative."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"f85ec3c8-2118-4696-a50e-9bb9fb14da85","name":"Sticky Note4","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-2048,-1184],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":816,"height":480,"content":"## Draft negative response\n\nFor negative sentiment, generates an empathetic email draft, strips formatting artifacts, and sends an internal Slack alert about the issue."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"92a5b552-5d95-46d1-a7b3-fdbd7211fa44","name":"Sticky Note5","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1120,-1056],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":432,"height":336,"content":"## Request human approval\n\nPosts the drafted negative-response email to Slack for human-in-the-loop review, waits for feedback, and checks whether the message was approved."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"2f9217b0-88a6-4039-b751-f70181969333","name":"Sticky Note6","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-544,-1024],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":544,"height":400,"content":"## Revise rejected draft\n\nIf the reviewer does not approve the draft, OpenAI revises the email and prepares the revised draft before looping it back to the Slack approval step."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"6897d6ae-4811-49c0-8fbb-5684e8da1f88","name":"Sticky Note7","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-656,-1584],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":496,"height":528,"content":"## Send negative follow-up\n\nAfter approval, resolves the final draft, sends the response to the respondent via Gmail, and logs the negative case to the CRM spreadsheet."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d04c00aa-6c87-4034-9511-790c6ecc15d1","name":"Sticky Note8","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-2000,-496],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":720,"height":528,"content":"## Handle positive response\n\nFor non-negative sentiment, generates and cleans a thank-you email, automatically sends it with Gmail, and logs the positive response to the CRM spreadsheet."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"5f8b8024-5a43-426b-a1a8-52db0eec616b","name":"When New Survey Response Arrives","type":"n8n-nodes-base.typeformTrigger","position":[-3248,-784],"webhookId":"survey-ai-triage-webhook","parameters":{"formId":"JDK9iZe5"},"credentials":{"typeformApi":{"id":"YvEbheFUL5lwNSLB","name":"Typeform account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"73568dda-21d7-43b3-b775-3928b517e69a","name":"Extract Survey Fields","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-3024,-784],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const items = $input.all();\nconst extractedData = items.map((item) => ({\n  name: item?.json[\"What is your full name?\"],\n  email: item?.json[\"What is your email address?\"],\n  rating: item?.json[\"How would you rate your overall experience?\"],\n  feedback: item?.json[\"Tell us about your experience in your own words.\"],\n}));\n\nreturn extractedData;\n"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"89e00348-61c7-41f9-880f-03008ef6305a","name":"AI Sentiment Classification","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[-2800,-784],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"messages":{"values":[{"content":"=You are a sentiment classifier. Read the following survey response and classify it as either 'positive' or 'negative'. Return ONLY the single word: positive or negative. No punctuation, no explanation.\n\nSurvey response: {{ $json.feedback }}\nRating (out of 5): {{ $json.rating }}"}]}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"aNcvBNwtqy155AK7","name":"n8n free OpenAI API credits"}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"ab99aba0-d263-40c9-b6d8-aff83d4e4617","name":"Remove Markdown Formatting","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-2448,-784],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const raw = $input.item.json.content || $input.item.json.text || $input.item.json.message?.content || '';\nconst cleaned = raw.replace(/```json\\n?|```/g, '').trim().toLowerCase();\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    ...$input.item.json,\n    sentiment: cleaned,\n    name: $('Extract Survey Fields').item.json.name,\n    email: $('Extract Survey Fields').item.json.email,\n    rating: $('Extract Survey Fields').item.json.rating,\n    feedback: $('Extract Survey Fields').item.json.feedback,\n    submissionDate: $('Extract Survey Fields').item.json.submissionDate\n  }\n};"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"9a9e5c70-a370-4db1-bba3-7217466d1d4f","name":"AI Draft Empathetic Reply","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[-2000,-880],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"messages":{"values":[{"content":"=You are a professional customer support specialist. A customer has submitted a negative survey response. Write a short, empathetic, and professional follow-up email to address their concerns.\n\nCustomer name: {{ $json.name }}\nCustomer rating: {{ $json.rating }} out of 5\nCustomer feedback: {{ $json.feedback }}\n\nWrite the email in this exact format:\nSubject: [email subject line]\n\n[email body]\n\nKeep the tone warm, empathetic, and solution-oriented. Do not promise anything you cannot deliver. Sign off as 'The Support Team'."}]}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"aNcvBNwtqy155AK7","name":"n8n free OpenAI API credits"}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"70eff816-6960-4cb3-9d5b-828589f5c3f5","name":"Cleanse Email Markdown","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-1648,-880],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const raw = $input.item.json.content || $input.item.json.text || $input.item.json.message?.content || '';\nconst cleaned = raw.replace(/```json\\n?|```/g, '').trim();\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    emailDraft: cleaned,\n    name: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.name,\n    email: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.email,\n    rating: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.rating,\n    feedback: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.feedback,\n    submissionDate: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.submissionDate,\n    sentiment: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.sentiment\n  }\n};"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"c20f51cf-1e19-4d70-92f2-7053c878cd4f","name":"Send and Await Slack Message","type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","position":[-1072,-880],"webhookId":"4c40203e-4f2e-440d-968a-8d3b769fd1f0","parameters":{"select":"channel","message":"=:email: *Email Draft for Review*\n\n*To:* {{ $json.email }}\n*Respondent:* {{ $json.name }}\n\n---\n{{ $json.emailDraft }}\n---\n\nReply *approved* to send this email, or describe what changes you'd like.","options":{"appendAttribution":false},"channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"email-review"},"operation":"sendAndWait","responseType":"freeText"},"credentials":{"slackApi":{"id":"b8wdNsL8ONX0cYcl","name":"Slack account"}},"typeVersion":2.2,"waitForResponse":true},{"id":"08b90fc8-e90a-4f5b-bc8a-d9a20e04082a","name":"AI Refine Email Draft","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[-496,-864],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini","cachedResultName":"GPT-4O-MINI"},"options":{},"messages":{"values":[{"content":"=You are a professional email writer. You wrote an email draft and a human reviewer has requested changes. Revise the email based on their feedback.\n\nOriginal email draft:\n{{ (() => { try { return $('Prepare Revised Email Draft').item.json.emailDraft; } catch (e) { return $('Cleanse Email Markdown').item.json.emailDraft; } })() }}\n\nHuman feedback:\n{{ $json.data.text }}\n\nWrite the revised email in this exact format:\nSubject: [email subject line]\n\n[email body]\n\nMaintain the same empathetic and professional tone. Sign off as 'The Support Team'."}]}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"aNcvBNwtqy155AK7","name":"n8n free OpenAI API credits"}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"9bb15ad3-a5b2-4402-8372-3162cd77afb7","name":"Prepare Revised Email Draft","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-144,-784],"parameters":{"jsCode":"let baseData;\ntry {\n  baseData = $('Prepare Revised Email Draft').item.json;\n} catch (e) {\n  baseData = $('Cleanse Email Markdown').item.json;\n}\n\nconst raw = $input.item.json.content || $input.item.json.text || $input.item.json.message?.content || '';\nconst cleaned = raw.replace(/```json\\n?|```/g, '').trim();\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    emailDraft: cleaned,\n    name: baseData.name,\n    email: baseData.email,\n    rating: baseData.rating,\n    feedback: baseData.feedback,\n    submissionDate: baseData.submissionDate,\n    sentiment: baseData.sentiment\n  }\n};"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"3163b1e7-853e-4406-bd1d-9b6ef5639615","name":"Send Email via Gmail","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[-464,-1424],"webhookId":"49e93fc8-5905-4820-b7e8-b7c2ee485b3b","parameters":{"sendTo":"={{ $json.email }}","message":"={{ $json.emailDraft.split('\\n').slice(2).join('\\n').trim() }}","options":{"appendAttribution":false},"subject":"={{ $json.emailDraft.split('\\n')[0].replace('Subject:', '').trim() }}","emailType":"text"},"credentials":{"gmailOAuth2":{"id":"FJgB2keJdukmOR4L","name":"Gmail account"}},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"cd243438-bcbe-4c02-8e1b-9c17a8244257","name":"Append Negative to CRM","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[-304,-1216],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Email":"={{ $('Finalize Email Draft').item.json.email }}","Sentiment":"={{ $('Finalize Email Draft').item.json.sentiment }}","Email Status":"=Sent","Respondent Name":"={{ $('Finalize Email Draft').item.json.name }}","Submission Date":"={{ $now.toFormat('dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm') }}","Timestamp Logged":"={{ $now.toFormat('dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm') }}"},"schema":[{"id":"Respondent Name","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Respondent Name","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Email","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Email","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Submission Date","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Submission Date","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Sentiment","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Sentiment","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Email Status","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Email Status","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Timestamp Logged","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Timestamp Logged","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true}],"mappingMode":"defineBelow","matchingColumns":[],"attemptToConvertTypes":false,"convertFieldsToString":false},"options":{},"operation":"append","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"support_crm"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"11JCQus9if5CsCNgIc1MU5YcAGJEjaXGs-xxHHCKBm3c"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsOAuth2Api":{"id":"m6jourNM2UWxyhZC","name":"Google Sheets account"}},"typeVersion":4.5,"continueOnFail":true},{"id":"7b561984-aa89-4d42-8cd9-b548640603fc","name":"AI Draft Thank-You Reply","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[-1952,-368],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"messages":{"values":[{"content":"=You are a professional customer success specialist. A customer has submitted a positive survey response. Write a short, warm, and genuine thank-you email.\n\nCustomer name: {{ $json.name }}\nCustomer rating: {{ $json.rating }} out of 5\nCustomer feedback: {{ $json.feedback }}\n\nWrite the email in this exact format:\nSubject: [email subject line]\n\n[email body]\n\nKeep the tone warm, genuine, and brief. Sign off as 'The Support Team'."}]}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"aNcvBNwtqy155AK7","name":"n8n free OpenAI API credits"}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"0208f0c5-b5a3-4354-9274-9cb358206f05","name":"Remove Markdown from Thanks","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-1616,-368],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const raw = $input.item.json.content || $input.item.json.text || $input.item.json.message?.content || '';\nconst cleaned = raw.replace(/```json\\n?|```/g, '').trim();\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    emailDraft: cleaned,\n    name: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.name,\n    email: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.email,\n    rating: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.rating,\n    feedback: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.feedback,\n    submissionDate: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.submissionDate,\n    sentiment: $('Remove Markdown Formatting').item.json.sentiment\n  }\n};"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"0c7ce2f9-33eb-4d54-bb27-945e62c1f701","name":"Send Thank-You via Gmail","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[-1424,-368],"webhookId":"f1f5b747-c42a-4789-8335-0996de31daad","parameters":{"sendTo":"={{ $json.email }}","message":"={{ $json.emailDraft.split('\\n').slice(2).join('\\n').trim() }}","options":{"appendAttribution":false},"subject":"={{ $json.emailDraft.split('\\n')[0].replace('Subject:', '').trim() }}","emailType":"text"},"credentials":{"gmailOAuth2":{"id":"FJgB2keJdukmOR4L","name":"Gmail account"}},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"ef7dce97-61c9-45f1-a995-74a58f400d84","name":"Append Positive to CRM","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[-1536,-144],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Email":"={{ $json.email }}","Sentiment":"={{ $json.sentiment }}","Email Status":"=Sent","Respondent Name":"={{ $json.name }}","Submission Date":"={{ $json.submissionDate }}","Timestamp Logged":"={{ $now.toFormat('dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm') }}"},"schema":[{"id":"Respondent Name","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Respondent Name","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Email","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Email","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Submission Date","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Submission Date","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Sentiment","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Sentiment","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Email Status","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Email Status","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Timestamp Logged","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Timestamp Logged","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true}],"mappingMode":"defineBelow","matchingColumns":[],"attemptToConvertTypes":false,"convertFieldsToString":false},"options":{},"operation":"append","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"support_crm"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"11JCQus9if5CsCNgIc1MU5YcAGJEjaXGs-xxHHCKBm3c"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsOAuth2Api":{"id":"m6jourNM2UWxyhZC","name":"Google Sheets account"}},"typeVersion":4.5,"continueOnFail":true},{"id":"047284e0-07d2-449a-951b-f03652385941","name":"Post Alert to Slack","type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","position":[-1376,-1056],"webhookId":"b45cd624-15d1-4d93-869d-ddd856029e89","parameters":{"text":"=:warning: *Negative Survey Response Received*\n\n*Respondent:* {{ $json.name }}\n*Email:* {{ $json.email }}\n*Rating:* {{ $json.rating }}/5\n*Feedback:* {{ $json.feedback }}\n\nA follow-up email draft is pending your review in #email-review.","select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"survey-alerts"},"otherOptions":{"includeLinkToWorkflow":false}},"credentials":{"slackApi":{"id":"b8wdNsL8ONX0cYcl","name":"Slack account"}},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"21780732-1945-449e-a721-fb7e19b80651","name":"If Email Gets Approval","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[-832,-880],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"version":3,"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":true,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"condition_approved","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"startsWith"},"leftValue":"={{ $json.data.text.trim() }}","rightValue":"approved"}]}},"typeVersion":2.3},{"id":"a7e2197f-33dc-4864-8e7b-6fa28b9b16b0","name":"Finalize Email Draft","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-608,-1216],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Determine which node actually produced the latest draft\n// Edit Fields runs on revision loops; Code: Strip Markdown 2 runs on first pass only\nlet draftData;\ntry {\n  draftData = $('Prepare Revised Email Draft').item.json;\n} catch (e) {\n  draftData = $('Cleanse Email Markdown').item.json;\n}\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    emailDraft: draftData.emailDraft,\n    name: draftData.name,\n    email: draftData.email,\n    rating: draftData.rating,\n    feedback: draftData.feedback,\n    submissionDate: draftData.submissionDate,\n    sentiment: draftData.sentiment\n  }\n};"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"4c84d52b-4f70-494c-a682-08757c736f58","name":"Set Workflow Configurations","type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","position":[-2720,-1232],"parameters":{"options":{},"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"cfg-typeform-form-id","name":"typeformFormId","type":"string","value":"JDK9iZe5"},{"id":"cfg-google-sheet-id","name":"googleSheetId","type":"string","value":"11JCQus9if5CsCNgIc1MU5YcAGJEjaXGs-xxHHCKBm3c"},{"id":"cfg-sheet-tab-name","name":"sheetTabName","type":"string","value":"support_crm"},{"id":"cfg-slack-channel-alerts","name":"slackChannelSurveyAlerts","type":"string","value":"survey-alerts"},{"id":"cfg-slack-channel-review","name":"slackChannelEmailReview","type":"string","value":"email-review"}]}},"typeVersion":3.4},{"id":"3bc15652-cbf8-42e1-84b4-f48e28ee78ff","name":"If Sentiment is Negative","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[-2224,-784],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"version":1,"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":true,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"condition_negative","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"},"leftValue":"={{ $json.sentiment }}","rightValue":"negative"}]}},"typeVersion":2}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"binaryMode":"separate","executionOrder":"v1"},"versionId":"c37e7f05-7bac-4806-bdd9-23b150abc564","nodeGroups":[],"connections":{"Finalize Email Draft":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Email via Gmail","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Append Negative to CRM","type":"main","index":0}]]},"AI Refine Email Draft":{"main":[[{"node":"Prepare Revised Email Draft","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract Survey Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"AI Sentiment Classification","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cleanse Email Markdown":{"main":[[{"node":"Post Alert to Slack","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Send and Await Slack Message","type":"main","index":0}]]},"If Email Gets Approval":{"main":[[{"node":"Finalize Email Draft","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"AI Refine Email Draft","type":"main","index":0}]]},"AI Draft Thank-You Reply":{"main":[[{"node":"Remove Markdown from Thanks","type":"main","index":0}]]},"If Sentiment is Negative":{"main":[[{"node":"AI Draft Empathetic Reply","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"AI Draft Thank-You Reply","type":"main","index":0}]]},"AI Draft Empathetic Reply":{"main":[[{"node":"Cleanse Email Markdown","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Remove Markdown Formatting":{"main":[[{"node":"If Sentiment is Negative","type":"main","index":0}]]},"AI Sentiment Classification":{"main":[[{"node":"Remove Markdown Formatting","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Prepare Revised Email Draft":{"main":[[{"node":"Send and Await Slack Message","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Remove Markdown from Thanks":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Thank-You via Gmail","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Append Positive to CRM","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send and Await Slack Message":{"main":[[{"node":"If Email Gets Approval","type":"main","index":0}]]},"When New Survey Response Arrives":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Survey Fields","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}